column2: SELECT g.objID, g.z, h.Flux_Ha_#, h.Flux_NII_#, h.Flux_Hb_#, h.Flux_OIII_#, h.Sigma_Ha_#, h.bpt, j.H_beta_flux, j.oiii_#_flux, j.H_alpha_flux, j.NII_#_flux, j.sigma_balmer, j.spectofiber, j.h_alpha_eqw into mydb.vas4 from galaxy g join dbo.fGetNearbyObjEq (#, #, #) as N ON N.objID = g.objID left outer join specobj y ON y.specobjID = g.specobjID left outer join emissionlinesport h ON h.specobjID = g.specobjID left outer join galspecline j ON j.specobjID = g.specobjID left outer join galspecextra f ON f.specobjID = g.specobjID
